{"tid":729104,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"王健是海航「爆買」操盤手　去世前長居香港　最後遺言：「腳痛」","createTime":"2018-07-04T09:32:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-04T17:30:40.000Z","uid":147314,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"c82bd7eb3b92d01b4ff5832bf1bc5ff24222b907","tid":729104,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T09:32:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://china.hket.com/article/2107812/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchina.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2107812%2F&d=hcKOE3i8VJxvkOAuUfaprV0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=9eb01b08\" target=\"_blank\">https://china.hket.com/article/2107812/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>王健是海航「爆買」操盤手 去世前長居香港</strong><br />\n<br />\n海航曾是中資海外併購的「四大天王」，而王健作為董事長，曾是海航集團參與這場「資本遊戲」的實際操盤手；而海航因海外爆賣深陷債務危機後，也由王健親自披甲上陣、收拾局面。據稱，他去世前兩年一直長居香港。<br />\n<br />\n王健是天津人，1983年畢業於中國民用航空學院經營管理專業，畢業後在中國民航局工作，跟海航另一位創始人陳峰一個辦公室。後來，他跟陳峰一起離職創辦海航。"},{"pid":"4fb7a56e667e6327094fe0dceaff8139146a89e1","tid":729104,"uid":147314,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T09:33:39.000Z","msg":"<strong>2016年前十大海外併購 海航佔三</strong><br />\n<br />\n據稱，在海航內部，陳峰叫他「王健同志」，他叫陳峰「陳總」。<br />\n<br />\n坊間傳聞指，雖然職位級別在陳峰之下，但在2016年年底發生過一次事件後，陳峰板越來越多時間花在研究佛學和老莊上，海航集團所有具體事務都是王健負責－－這也包括發生在2017年年底的海航流動性危機，連負面新聞都是王健親自上陣協調的。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static01.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2105000/2107812/phot_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2105000%2F2107812%2Fphot_1024.jpg&h=edcd0fda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ 海航曾是中資海外併購的「四大天王」，而王健作為董事長，曾是海航集團參與這場「資本遊戲」的實際操盤手。"},{"pid":"c7cf2f215db98997e95a2ee8f1dbc2ad6426595b","tid":729104,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T09:34:03.000Z","msg":"據了解，在2015至2017年間，海航和萬達、復星、安邦一起，成為海外併購「四大天王」。王健帶領的海航是最「進取」的，2016年前十大海外併購交易中，海航系佔據了3席，海航累計海外投資高達450億美元。"},{"pid":"1a20bfd98d50723d5d0898a2b38c0a8d367c2030","tid":729104,"uid":147314,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T09:34:28.000Z","msg":"<strong>上月14日最後露面 死時在法遊覽<br />\n</strong><br />\n王健最後一次出現在公開場合是6月14日。當時海南省政協主席毛萬春去海航集團調研，與陳峰、王健及相關單位負責人進行座談交流。<br />\n<br />\n但在半個月後，他在法國普羅旺斯的阿維尼翁遊覽時不幸摔下，陷入昏迷。據財新報道，他最後一句話是對醫生說的，「腳疼」。<br />\n<br />\n海航今天稍早前發出的訃告稱，王健「在法國公務考察時意外跌落導致重傷，經搶救無效，於當地時間2018年7月3日不幸離世，享年57歲」。"},{"pid":"04b65b5eb68a77f29454b0d455208d472ecca739","tid":729104,"uid":511,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T09:35:45.000Z","msg":"被跌死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc806e2798d6f2055977537ad63a7f0846400ff3","tid":729104,"uid":53466,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T09:36:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1e000f35dac5f8c5352f8fd6e6591076e796f940","tid":729104,"uid":73915,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T09:36:23.000Z","msg":"以死相搏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1aefb35d4d9b41e33d190da571aa88b3009b2c59","tid":729104,"uid":57633,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T09:37:21.000Z","msg":"買通法國佬啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be138fbb4e4de74147acf4670b97f7c3f5b7a38c","tid":729104,"uid":58552,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T09:37:30.000Z","msg":"海航沒事了"},{"pid":"25af192846829553416af2640832b63b1000e0c2","tid":729104,"uid":19126,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T09:38:02.000Z","msg":"腳痛而死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e4c2e7b0dd60b42391f1b7889bf79323afe22aa","tid":729104,"uid":48083,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"1a20bfd98d50723d5d0898a2b38c0a8d367c2030","tid":729104,"uid":147314,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T09:34:28.000Z","msg":"<strong>上月14日最後露面 死時在法遊覽<br />\n</strong><br />\n王健最後一次出現在公開場合是6月14日。當時海南省政協主席毛萬春去海航集團調研，與陳峰、王健及相關單位負責人進行座談交流。<br />\n<br />\n但在半個月後，他在法國普羅旺斯的阿維尼翁遊覽時不幸摔下，陷入昏迷。據財新報道，他最後一句話是對醫生說的，「腳疼」。<br />\n<br />\n海航今天稍早前發出的訃告稱，王健「在法國公務考察時意外跌落導致重傷，經搶救無效，於當地時間2018年7月3日不幸離世，享年57歲」。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T09:38:42.000Z","msg":"咁有錢都唔請個好啲編劇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"064bee7c50b13e0345055b5b92bdbbf1ccc84f9d","tid":729104,"uid":65604,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T09:39:24.000Z","msg":"會係會係影武者，真的係南美洲整緊容<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13a02c7e6a08a872e19aadf1f3360cb247d6e054","tid":729104,"uid":38666,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"25af192846829553416af2640832b63b1000e0c2","tid":729104,"uid":19126,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T09:38:02.000Z","msg":"腳痛而死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T09:39:44.000Z","msg":"同董伯伯一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50b77aabba5f99c81be64ac2b783f0755ee3d5df","tid":729104,"uid":35014,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T09:44:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9ab152c405ac8f7793ca78d2eed762d26da6ae31","tid":729104,"uid":52276,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"50b77aabba5f99c81be64ac2b783f0755ee3d5df","tid":729104,"uid":35014,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T09:44:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T09:48:19.000Z","msg":"咪即係落馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0eeb03b42ba6dbced4d6cb35c9d64318e17369a7","tid":729104,"uid":133522,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"50b77aabba5f99c81be64ac2b783f075